'''Jalaluddin Thaib''' (laia di Jorong Subarang, [[Balingka]], [[IV Koto, Agam|IV Koto]], [[Agam]], 1895 – maningga di [[Lubuak Basuang]], Agam, [[Sumatera Barat]], 1959 pado umuar 64 taun) adolah surang [[ulama]], tokoh pandidikan sarato pajuang kamardekaan [[Indonesia]].<ref>[http://www.scribd.com/doc/72623401/JALALUDDIN-THAIB JALALUDDIN THAIB (1895–1959)] Scribd Inc. Diakses 13 Mei 2013.</ref>

Baliau adolah salah surang dari tigo sarangkai [[Persatuan Muslim Indonesia]] (Permi) basamo jo [[Muchtar Lutfi]] sarato [[Ilyas Ya'kub]]. Jalaluddin pernah dibuang ka [[Digul]] dek panjajah [[Balando]] karano kagiatan pajuangannyo dianggap babahayo dek pihak panjajah.<ref>[http://books.google.co.id/books?id=KL8MEwzjSBoC&pg=PA80&lpg=PA80&dq=Jalaluddin+Thaib&source=bl&ots=Ezvnd7uJOd&sig=y_l2u4NSWkQYYHkGM6MbTZwhS5Y&hl=en&sa=X&ei=-QpBUbiYJsPJrAfyhYGYCQ&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Jalaluddin%20Thaib&f=false Ulama perempuan Indonesia] Edited by Jajat Burhanuddin, Gramedia Pustaka Utama. Diakses 13 Mei 2013.</ref>

